  "Koo Bon-neung runs Heesung Electronics, which makes display components for TVs, computers, tablets and smartphones. ",
  "He is the younger brother of Koo Bon-moo, the late chairman of the LG Group, one of the top five conglomerates in South Korea. ",
  "In 2004 his son Koo Kwang-moo was adopted by his brother who lost his own son in a car accident. Kwang-moo now helms LG as its chairman. "
